A: You can use the following code to convert a bitmap to a base64 string.
String base64String = null;

Bitmap bitmap = Bitmap.getBitmapResource("image.png");
ByteArrayOutputStream baos = new ByteArrayOutputStream();
bitmap.copy(Bitmap.CopyMode.NORMAL, baos);
byte[] bytes = baos.toByteArray();
base64String = Base64.encodeToString(bytes, Base64.DEFAULT);
